rows.label: bf01120100_0010
rows.name:
Wheeling out the Maelstrom for this?
Bahn sure has deep pockets...

rows.label: bf01120100_0020
rows.name: Gawking at a boat this size?

rows.label: bf01120100_0040
rows.name: What's my age got to do with anything?

rows.label: bf01120100_0050
rows.name:
I can tell an awesome feat of
engineering when I see one!

rows.label: bf01120100_0060
rows.name: Just meant that your ignorance is astounding.

rows.label: bf01120100_0070
rows.name: What's her problem? We're nearly the same age.

rows.label: bf01120100_0080
rows.name:
Also, you might wanna watch where you
stand, otherwise when we cast off...

rows.label: bf01120100_0090
rows.name: that rope'll take your leg off.

rows.label: bf01120100_0130
rows.name: Now who's the ignorant one here?

rows.label: bf01120100_0150
rows.name:
Rex, we're heading out.
There's no one seeing you off, right?

rows.label: bf01120100_0160
rows.name:
You got night watch.
Till then, rest up inside.
